Newport Corp sets increase in shr buyback . Newport Corp said on Friday its board had approved an additional 200 , 000 shares for repurchase under a share buyback program initiated in April . This brings the total number of shares authorized for repurchase to 290 , 000 under the program , of which 76 , 000 have been repurchased to date , the company said . It said the shares will be used for its stock option , restricted stock and employee stock purchase plans . Newport had 8 . 9 million shares in common stock outstanding as of March 31 . 
